<category><![CDATA[The Book of Mormon]]></category>
<category><![CDATA[Gospel Study]]></category>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/study/manual/come-follow-me-for-home-and-church-book-of-mormon-2024/10?lang=eng</guid>
